FBIS4-60778 "drsov084_v_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 Lithuania President Receives Telegram From Ukraine's Kravchuk President Receives Telegram From Ukraine's Kravchuk WS0205083894 Vilnius ELTA in English 1948 GMT 29 Apr 94 WS0205083894 Vilnius ELTA English BFN [From "News Bulletin" No. 488] [Text] Vilnius, April 29, ELTA -- Ukrainian President Leonid Kravchuk sent a telegram to his Lithuanian counterpart Algirdas Brazauskas saying he welcomed Lithuanian-Polish friendship and co- operation treaty. Kravchuk said in the telegram: "I am sure the important political act will have positive influence on the further development of Lithuanian-Polish relations and on the strengthening of confidence, security and stability atmosphere in the European continent".
